definitions.definition: A newspaper or magazine with many pictures, or section thereof.
An article primarily featuring many photographs, or simply a collection of photographs.
examples: The budding starlet is featured in a pictorial in a glossy magazine next week.

definitions.definition: A stamp featuring a vignette of local scenery or culture.

main_definition: A newspaper or magazine with many pictures, or section thereof.
secondary_definitions: An article primarily featuring many photographs, or simply a collection of photographs.
( philately ) A stamp featuring a vignette of local scenery or culture.
